		<li>Separated for each onepiece-framework application.</li>
	</ul>
	
	<h2>How to use for Cookie class</h2>
	<p>How to use is very easy.</p>
	<div class="code">
		<code>
		&lt;php
		//	Get method is get saved cookie value. 2nd arguments is default value.
		$count = Cookie::Get('count', 0); 
		
		//	Set method is save to cookie value.
		Cookie::Get('count', $count);
		</code>
	</div>
